  <brief_title>Effects of Different Assisted Mechanical Ventilation in Acute Lung Injury (ALI)/Acute Respiratory Distress Syndrome (ARDS) Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Different Assisted Mechanical Ventilation in ALI/ARDS Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
